31:23.913 --> 31:24.434
Thirdly.

31:25.410 --> 31:32.818
When I read the book of Obadiah and I see God's judgment against a neighboring country that should have been their brother's keeper, I'm reminded, I need to love mercy.

31:33.299 --> 31:34.039
