32:19.012 --> 32:19.853
And the final takeaway.

32:21.615 --> 32:24.818
Even when circumstances seem out of control,

32:26.018 --> 32:31.804
And it seems like hopeless, bleak, and you don't even know if tomorrow will come.

32:33.065 --> 32:38.690
